'''Google Play Pass'''是[[Google|Google]]推出的[[电子游戏|游戏]]和[[应用程序|应用]][[訂閱|订阅服务]]，適用於{{link-en|Android}}设备。它于2019年9月23日在美国率先推出<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Google Play Pass bundles 350 Android games and apps for $4.99 per month|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/23/20878843/google-play-pass-bundles-350-android-games-and-apps-for-4-99-per-month|accessdate=|author=Webster|date=September 23, 2019|first=Andrew|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231160558/https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/23/20878843/google-play-pass-bundles-350-android-games-and-apps-for-4-99-per-month|archivedate=2020-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年7月，该服务在[[德国|德国]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]等國陸續開通<ref>{{Cite web|title=Spieleabo: Google Play Pass auf Android eröffnet|url=http://www.golem.de/news/spieleabo-google-play-pass-auf-android-eroeffnet-1909-144045.html|accessdate=July 15, 2020|author=Peter Steinlechner|date=July 8, 2020|publisher=golem.de|language=de|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020010159/https://www.golem.de/news/spieleabo-google-play-pass-auf-android-eroeffnet-1909-144045.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mobile Games: Spieleabo Google Play Pass startet in Deutschland|url=http://www.golem.de/news/mobile-games-spieleabo-google-play-pass-startet-in-deutschland-2007-149647.html|accessdate=July 15, 2020|author=Peter Steinlechner|date=July 14, 2020|publisher=golem.de|language=de|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907203006/https://www.golem.de/news/mobile-games-spieleabo-google-play-pass-startet-in-deutschland-2007-149647.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

订阅者只需按月或按年支付訂閱費，便能使用訂閱服務所包含的460多种应用和游戏，而无需觀看广告和应用内額外购买。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Google Play Pass|url=https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/about/play-pass/|accessdate=July 16, 2020|work=Google Play Pass|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225032550/https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/about/play-pass/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Here are 460 apps and games available on Google Play Pass right now|url=https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/06/26/google-play-pass-apps-games-list/|accessdate=June 29, 2020|date=June 26, 2020|publisher=Android Police|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719180748/https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/06/26/google-play-pass-apps-games-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
